{"id":"477031","title":"我为养家忙！[穿越]","writer":"江北小酥肉","dateline":"1546383202","updatetime":"1546383202","isover":"1","filesize":"581265","linecount":"5479","wordcount":"191681","imgpath":"https://photos.smugmug.com/photos/i-7TqQDhn/0/84ccf6b1/O/i-7TqQDhn.jpg","hash":"woweiyangjiamang","urlhash":"txtnvl_3852239","sign":"","desc":"晋江VIP2018-11-15完结\n当前被收藏数：2643 营养液数：195 文章积分：33,064,982 \n文案\n唐轶从末世穿越到异世农家，心如死水，原主懒惰成性，活活把自己给饿死了，于是他决定效仿一下。\n挨饿的第一天，一个容貌昳丽的小哥敲开了他的门，向他讨一碗水。\n当晚，这人又要来借半张床。\n数日之后，试图饿死自己的唐轶被踹下了床。\n因为他家夫郎饿了。\n唐轶只得烧柴温水，洗菜煮饭，再没时间想该怎么死了。\ntips:\n1.生崽。\n2.比较慢的种田文。\n·\n内容标签： 穿越时空 种田文 美食 甜文\n搜索关键字：主角：唐轶（攻），谢世迎（受） ┃ 配角： ┃ 其它：\n[domain]","hot":"0","num":"0","cid":"170","suggcate":"耽美重生,穿越,耽美,种田文,重生","suggcids":"170,14,25,166,117","notbook":"0","fetchv":"0","lasthot":"0","clicknum":"0","isvip":"1","ish":"0","age":"古代","channel":"女","isqiniu":"0","list":"0,1t9,3ri,5sz,7ns,9mf,bno,dov,fos,hnl,jlc,lh2,nja,plk,rj7,thj,vj5,xke,zpo,11rl,142k,1697,185w,1act,1cpo,1f7q,1hdc,1ji8,1lvs,1o0s,1qgv,1smd,1uqz,1wzi,1z6i,21cf,23pl,25ug,27st,29yn,2c30,2e44,2gau,2icc,2kjx,2mki,2os5,2r3h,2tes,2vpu,2xyv,30dg,32t1,34z1,374l,397c,3ba0,3dbv,3fka,3htu,3k4c,3m8t,3onp,3qsd,3sy5,3v29,3wtp,3yez,40b5,429e,44dx,46pc,48oo,4app,4cmx,4emx,4gif,4ihq,4ki5,4mkw,4oq3,4qjl,4sfx,4uih,4wbt,4ylb,50qf,52mh,54ed,56p7,58uc,5azk,5d0q,5eyc,5h46,5iz5,5ktu,5msp,5orh,5qog,5scj,5tt2,5vny,5xqu,5ze1,616h,62v4,64lp,664d,66v0","pages":"109","errors":"0","stars":"0","starcounts":"0","isbroken":"0","iswx":"1","leader":"唐轶|谢世迎|冯如海","txturl":"https://photos.smugmug.com/photos/i-6v4Tnbc/0/f477da90/1500x1500/i-6v4Tnbc-1500x1500.png","startpos":"8830"}